These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, havana, oliveros, fonseca
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, board-games, chess, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the game-smoker##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
4. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
5. the fonseca-smoker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the havana-smoker##5
7. the havana-smoker is somewhere between the game-smoker and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
8. the havana-smoker and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks have the same parity positions##9
9. the oliveros-smoker and the person who's hobby is video-games have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | game | havana | oliveros     | fonseca |
| Pet           | chess   | magic-tricks     | board-games | video-games  |

