.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, bus, skateboard, train
House: gothic-revival, colonial, ranch-style, townhouse
1. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the townhouse house and the person driving the bus have the same parity positions##9
3. the colonial house is not to the right of the ranch-style house##8
4. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the person driving the train##8
5. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
6. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the colonial house##5
7. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
8. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | train     | skateboard    | subway | bus    |
| Hobby      | gothic-revival | colonial | ranch-style      | townhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, oliveros, cain, alhambra
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, march, january, april
1. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
6. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
8. the oliveros-smoker and the person who's birthday is in march have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | oliveros    | cain   | siglo    | alhambra  |
| Food       | march | april | october | january |

