.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
House: palace, art-deco, colonial, cottage
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, chaman, bolivar, aristoff
1. the fonseca-smoker is the art-deco house##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
5. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the palace house##1
6. the cottage house and the aristoff-smoker have the same parity positions##9
7. the colonial house is on the left or right of the palace house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | cottage | colonial | palace  | art-deco |
| Music-Genre   | bolivar             | chaman          | aristoff | fonseca    |

