.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, iris, poppy
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, animation, western, sports
1. the person who growsiris is not the person watching western movies##6
2. the person watching time-travel movies and the person who growsdaffodil have different parity positions##9
3. the person watching animation movies and the person who growsrose have different parity positions##9
4. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
6. the person who growsrose is not the person watching animation movies##6
7. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
9. the person watching sports movies is not the person who growspoppy##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | daffodil | iris | poppy  | rose |
| Pet           | animation   | time-travel     | western | sports      |

