.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, rabbit, cat
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, skydiving, reading, collecting
1. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
4. the person who's hobby is singing and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9
5. the owner of the cat and the person who's hobby is singing have different parity positions##9
6. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
8. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | pony | turtle | rabbit | cat |
| Nationality   | collecting        | reading    | singing   | skydiving |

