2. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes ebony and the person who likes red##2
3. the person who likes ivory and the owner of the mouse have different parity positions##9
4. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
5. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
