4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing poker is not the american##6
6. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
7. the person playing bridge and the nigerian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
