.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, canasta, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, ice-hockey, water-polo, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
2. the person playing chess and the person who's sport is volleyball have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
4. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
5. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is volleyball##7
6. the person playing chess is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | canasta | whist   | mah-jongg | chess |
| Transport   | water-polo   | ice-hockey | tennis    | volleyball      |

