.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, january, december
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, montecristo, chaman, bolivar
 1. the person who's birthday is in march and the chaman-smoker have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in july##7
 4. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
 6. the chaman-smoker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in december and the montecristo-smoker have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
 9. the bolivar-smoker is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | july  | december | january  | march |
| Music-Genre   | bolivar | chaman     | ritmeester | montecristo     |

