.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, thriller, martial-arts, action
City: prague, new-york, miami, venice
 1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 3. the person traveling to venice is not to the right of the person traveling to miami##8
 4. the person traveling to new-york is in an odd position##4
 5. the person traveling to prague is not the person watching thriller movies##6
 6. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person watching sports movies##8
 7. the person watching action movies and the person traveling to new-york have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
 9. the person watching action movies is the person traveling to new-york##1
10. the person watching thriller movies and the person traveling to new-york have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | thriller    | martial-arts        | action   | sports      |
| Hobby      | venice | miami | new-york | prague |

 